  "title": {
   "en": "Kao ga Miwakerarenai Hakushaku Reijou Desu ga, Akunin Koushaku-sama ni Dekiai Sarete Imasu"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "顔が見分けられない伯爵令嬢ですが、悪人公爵様に溺愛されています@COMIC"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "As the daughter of a count, Sarah is unable to socialize and is ostracized by aristocratic society because she has a condition which prevents her from recognizing faces. She is despised by her family and marries the infamous \"Duke of Evil\" as a substitute for her sister. Calyx is feared as an unfair husband, but he is actually the complete opposite of that! She received a gift of a custom-made dress and a first date holding her hand with a kind word that made her bewildered. For the first time in her life, he treated her like a princess, and the burn mark on his face, which everyone abhors, became the only mark that could distinguish him from others and endear him to her.",
   "ja": "顔を見分けられない病を持つ伯爵令嬢サラは、社交の場での失敗をきっかけに、家族からぞんざいな扱いを受ける日々を過ごしていた。そんなある日、妹の身代わりに、醜い火傷痕を持ち『悪人公爵』と恐れられるカリクスとの結婚を命じられる。しかし、嫁ぎ先でサラが出会った彼は噂と全く違っていた！？\n\n「君には笑っていてほしい」\n\nカリクスの優しさに触れ、徐々に自信を取り戻していくサラだったが、かつて社交界で最大の失態を犯した相手に再会してしまい――？"
  },
